          "reviewBody": "Our experience at mindseed was excellent. Special thanks to Principal Ma'am and Nirmala Teacher for always being supportive and providing utmost care to our daughter and all other staff members at the institute. In today's competitive world schools like mindseed are very rare to be found, we were lucky. It has not only encouraged my child but also us, her parents Thank you once again",
