          "reviewBody": "Hello Ma'am\nIt was an amazing and  mesmorising event 👏\nThe \"ECHO\" theam was absolutely amazing...\n\nKudos to the efforts taken by teaching n non teaching staff 👍🏻\nIt was very nice to see our child performing on stage without any fear, it's possible only bcoz of all staff 😀",
