            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I want to extend my most heartfelt appreciation to the teachers , staff members and the students for the pleasant and charming annual day morning.\nIt was an amazing show with amusing dances, sensational songs and great performances all with the effort and team work of the devoted teachers.\nIt was a memorable day for me as it was my child first live performannce which would always be cherished.\nWe are really fortunate to have our kid here in this wonderful school.\n#Annualday2023",
